title: Tant Anci och Froken Sara
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, Take-out, European, Swedish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Ecological cafe, boutique, and takeaway. Menu includes several vegetarian choices and some vegan ones, including vegan burger, lentil salad with bread, sandwiches, and a few vegan pastries. There is a starter that can be made vegan as well upon request. Everyday a vegetarian soup that's sometimes vegan suitable, offered from 11:00-14:00. Free Wi-Fi.
